{"word":"H560 - אֲמַר - ʼămar - am-ar' - Command","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אֲמַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʼămar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>am-ar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Command"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"சொல், பேசு, கட்டளையிடு, விவரி, தெரிவி, கேள் - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"(P'al) to say, to speak, to command, to tell, to relate"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> (Chaldee); corresponding to <a href=\"#/H559 - אָמַר - ʼâmar - aw-mar'/559\">H559</a>: - command, declare, say, speak, tell."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3983 - מֵאמַר - mêʼmar - may-mar'/3983\">H3983</a>, <a href=\"#/H560 - אֲמַר - ʼămar - am-ar'/560\">H560</a>, <a href=\"#/H563 - אִמַּר - ʼimmar - im-mar'/563\">H563</a>"}]}